values:
Well I am in Florida Right now, I know i havent updated since i first got this journal but i plan on trying to update as much as i can now, Me and Chris have to leave this piece at like 2 in the morning for the orlando airport our plane leaves at 5:50 so that sucks.  I need weed now i havent had it in my system for like 6 days which is very unusual for me. oh well probably good for me though.  Im ready to go home and smoke a bowl though, i actually miss bloomington, i really dont know why but i do, funny. I wish I had some speed or something i am tired and no point to sleep till i get home.  It sucks because I kind of got a little tan.  But it is uneven, my left arm is still white and my right arm is tan maybe im half one pigment and half another. That would be cool.   Fuck i am bored its raining outside otherwise i would be out on the dock or trying to catch these lizards that are every where in Florida there like fucking insects here weird.  I have had a great time but ready to get home.  
                                        -peace- Ghostwriter

Well I found out what skee skee skee is from Mike the other day! So atleast I can say I have learned something at school this week.  So now that I know what it is I have been singing that alot and letting everybody I come in contact with know what it is too. For any reader who arent familiar with skee skee it is when a guy blows his load, (ejaculates). Interesting huh, I wonder if the rapper knew that?
Anyways its early and I am ready to have my morning smoke with Chris, Logan, and Chris R. We are meeting somewhere!
I like this, now its easier to talk to myself

This Sucks, i have so much to do to catch up in CW(Creative Writing).  Have have it third hour(oh wait i am supposed to be in there right now but instead i am being a retard and trying to avoid it because i have things due. Oh well I guess I have to face it I am a slacker. Once a slacker always a slacker.

Last Night fucking rocked. Me and Chris went to see LOTR Return of the King ripped of our asses.  I havent been that high for along time. And its my first time smoking and then going to see a movie.It was fun. Then we went to Chris's house and ate. while he jammed on the guitar and i played what notes i know on a keyboard.
-Peace- , GhostWriter
